title: Homepage loading slowly
description: The homepage of the website takes too long to load, causing users to leave the site before it fully renders.

title: Broken links in the footer
description: Several links in the footer of the website are broken, leading to 404 errors when clicked.

title: Incorrect product pricing
description: Product prices are not reflecting correctly on the website, causing confusion among customers during checkout.

title: Responsive design issue on mobile devices
description: The website's layout breaks on certain mobile devices, making it difficult to navigate and use.

title: Login functionality not working
description: Users are unable to log in to their accounts on the website, preventing access to member-only features.

title: SSL certificate expired
description: The SSL certificate for the website has expired, resulting in security warnings for visitors.

title: Images not loading in the gallery
description: Images in the website's gallery fail to load, leaving blank spaces on the page.

title: Contact form submission error
description: When users submit the contact form, they receive an error message and their messages are not delivered.

title: Typography inconsistency
description: There are inconsistencies in typography throughout the website, affecting readability and visual coherence.

title: Broken search functionality
description: The search feature on the website returns irrelevant results or no results at all, hindering user navigation.

title: Missing meta descriptions
description: Many pages on the website lack meta descriptions, affecting SEO performance and search engine rankings.

title: Accessibility issues for screen readers
description: The website is not fully accessible for users relying on screen readers, violating accessibility standards.

title: Checkout process freezes intermittently
description: During the checkout process, the website freezes intermittently, preventing users from completing their purchases.

title: Incorrect contact information
description: The contact information displayed on the website is outdated or incorrect, leading to communication issues with customers.

title: Broken navigation menu
description: The navigation menu on the website is broken, making it difficult for users to navigate between pages.

title: Payment gateway integration issue
description: There is an issue with integrating the payment gateway, causing errors during the payment process.

title: Broken social media links
description: Links to the website's social media profiles are broken, leading to error pages or incorrect destinations.

title: Security vulnerability in login system
description: A security vulnerability has been identified in the website's login system, potentially exposing user data to risks.
